{"id":510,"date":"2017-06-26T10:59:25","date_gmt":"2017-06-26T03:29:25","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/maylocnuochydrogen.com\/?p=203"},"modified":"2017-06-26T10:59:25","modified_gmt":"2017-06-26T03:29:25","slug":"tac-dung-tuyet-voi-cua-nuoc-hydrogen-trong-viec-dieu-tri-viem-da-va-cac-benh-lien-quan-ngoai-da","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/maylocnuoc1.webtudong8giay.com\/tac-dung-tuyet-voi-cua-nuoc-hydrogen-trong-viec-dieu-tri-viem-da-va-cac-benh-lien-quan-ngoai-da\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Hydrogen trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb vi\u00eam da v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh li\u00ean quan ngo\u00e0i da"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e2u nay \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a <a href=\"http:\/\/maylocnuochydrogen.com\/\">n\u01b0\u1edbc Hydrogen<\/a> ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Hydrogen v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da, Spa, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n l\u1edbn. \u0110\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ngu\u1ed3n n\u01b0\u1edbc Hydrogen \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb vi\u00eam da v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn da, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f9ng \u0111i v\u00e0o t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n<h3><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-204 size-full\" title=\"tac-dung-tuyet-voi-cua-nuoc-hydrogen-trong-viec-dieu-tri-viem-da-va-cac-benh-lien-quan-ngoai-da\" src=\"http:\/\/maylocnuochydrogen.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/06\/benh-viem-da-co-dia-co-lay-khong-1.jpg\" alt=\"tac-dung-tuyet-voi-cua-nuoc-hydrogen-trong-viec-dieu-tri-viem-da-va-cac-benh-lien-quan-ngoai-da\" width=\"500\" height=\"328\" \/><br \/>\n<strong>Vi\u00eam da v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn da<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Vi\u00eam da do c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba hay vi\u00eam da do d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n m\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea5n hoa, th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. C\u00e1c hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng vi\u00eam ad c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 vi\u00eam da d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng, vi\u00eam k\u1ebft m\u1ea1c d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng, vi\u00eam m\u0169i d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng, s\u1ed1t theo m\u00f9a hay hen suy\u1ec5n. Vi\u00eam da l\u00e0 h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch do c\u00e1c oxy ho\u1ea1t h\u00f3a (g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do).<\/p>\n<h3><\/h3>\n<h3><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-205 size-full\" title=\"tac-dung-tuyet-voi-cua-nuoc-hydrogen-trong-viec-dieu-tri-viem-da-va-cac-benh-lien-quan-ngoai-da\" src=\"http:\/\/maylocnuochydrogen.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/06\/cach-tri-viem-da-co-dia-nhanh-khong-tai-phat-1.jpg\" alt=\"tac-dung-tuyet-voi-cua-nuoc-hydrogen-trong-viec-dieu-tri-viem-da-va-cac-benh-lien-quan-ngoai-da\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" \/><\/h3>\n<h3><strong>T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ki\u1ec1m Hydrogen trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb vi\u00eam da v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh li\u00ean quan ngo\u00e0i da<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ki\u1ec1m Hydrogen ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00e1c g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ec7nh vi\u00eam da, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecb ng\u1ee9a hay h\u1eaft h\u01a1i, ch\u00e0m b\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec5m (Eczema). Vi\u00eam da th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 da kh\u00f4, v\u00ec th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m \u1ea9m da l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng.<br \/>\nTh\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngu\u1ed3n n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee9a kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f4i ngo\u00e0i ra, v\u1ec7 sinh ra gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho da, ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ef1 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a vi khu\u1ea9n l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb vi\u00eam da th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ec7nh nh\u00e2n n\u00ean \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-206 size-full\" title=\"tac-dung-tuyet-voi-cua-nuoc-hydrogen-trong-viec-dieu-tri-viem-da-va-cac-benh-lien-quan-ngoai-da\" src=\"http:\/\/maylocnuochydrogen.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/06\/cach-uong-nuoc-dung-cach-giup-giam-can-hieu-qua-3-1.jpg\" alt=\"tac-dung-tuyet-voi-cua-nuoc-hydrogen-trong-viec-dieu-tri-viem-da-va-cac-benh-lien-quan-ngoai-da\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" \/><br \/>\nU\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Hydrogen h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf clorin t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean da m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n cung c\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/p>\n<p>kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da kh\u1ecfe, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. T\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c u\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Hydrogen m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, tuy nhi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i sau do \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da t\u1eeb Hydrogen c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i.<br \/>\n\u0110\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Hydrogen \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n u\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y thay cho n\u01b0\u1edbc tinh khi\u1ebft. V\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb m\u00e1y l\u1ecdc n\u01b0\u1edbc Hydrogen Kangaroo \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n n\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, tr\u1ecb vi\u00eam da v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-208 size-full\" title=\"tac-dung-tuyet-voi-cua-nuoc-hydrogen-trong-viec-dieu-tri-viem-da-va-cac-benh-lien-quan-ngoai-da\" src=\"http:\/\/maylocnuochydrogen.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/06\/cach-giam-can-bang-uong-nuoc-loc-cuc-hieu-qua-va-don-gian-1.jpg\" alt=\"tac-dung-tuyet-voi-cua-nuoc-hydrogen-trong-viec-dieu-tri-viem-da-va-cac-benh-lien-quan-ngoai-da\" width=\"450\" height=\"266\" \/><br \/>\nNgo\u00e0i ra, u\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee9a kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t Hydrogen ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, c\u00e1c m\u00f4 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da, gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m. Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Hydrogen trong l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p an to\u00e0n, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t cho m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n da t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb theo th\u1eddi gian<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e2u nay \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Hydrogen ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Hydrogen v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da, Spa, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":205,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[3],"tags":[14,5,6,19],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/maylocnuoc1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/510"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/maylocnuoc1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/maylocnuoc1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/maylocnuoc1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/maylocnuoc1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=510"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/maylocnuoc1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/510\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/maylocnuoc1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/maylocnuoc1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=510"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/maylocnuoc1